<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Facilities</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel three-sm">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p>Pilgrim Hospital, Boston is a large district general hospital located on the outskirts of Boston.<br/>The majority of hosptial services are provided from the hospital's main 9-storey tower block, although there is also extensive additional accomodation.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="page-links">
<p>On this page:</p>
