<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentea332ffc80954121a21e1ed68617ab4c">
</div>
<p>Pilgrim Hospital has a full-time chaplaincy team which provides a range of services.<br/><br/>The hospital Chapel is situated on the ground floor. The Chapel is open throughout the day and night and is available to patients, their families/carers and staff for times of quiet, prayer and reflection. <br/><br/></p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
