<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent8cebe5dc1ca14e40a98f5f5d4ad7f22d">
</div>
<p>Patient car parking at Pilgrim Hospital, Boston costs £1.70 for 0-1 hours, £4.20 for 1-4 hours and £5 for over 4 hours. A daily charge of £1.90 per day has been implemented for Blue Badge  		holders. Concessions are available for those receiving some benefits, cancer patients and regular visitors.</p>
<p>You can also pay using the <a href="https://www.ulh.nhs.uk/content/uploads/2018/11/good2go.pdf">good2go</a> app.</p>
